Leap

Its back moves as（随着） your back moves.
Its arms moves as your arms move.
Its seat moves as your seat moves.
It's first chair that actually changes shape to
mimic（模仿） and support the movement of your spine（脊柱）.
Thanks to its advanced technology and extraordinary comfort,
the Leap chair is a proven technology...
a healthier way to sit.

--- Adjustable Headrest（头靠）* ---
Grasp the headrest and move up and down to adjust the height
to meet your preferred level of comfort.

--- Adjustable lumbar（腰椎） ---
For additional back support, grab both handles（把手） and slide up or down.
Position the lumbar to fit comfortably into the curve of your lower back.

--- Lower back firmness（硬度/支撑程度） ---
Turn the knob forward to increase firmness.
Turn the knob backward to decrease firmness.

--- Seat Height ---
To raise the chair, lift your body weight and pull lever(控制杆) up.
To lower the chair, stay seated and pull lever up.

--- Variable Back Stop ---
Set recline（下躺） angle by rotating the paddle（桨） to any of the five positions.
When the paddle is hori`zontal, the back will allow you to fully recline.

--- Height/Width/Pivot/Depth/Adjustable arms ---
Lift button under arm caps(扶手板) to adjust height.
To adjust arm cap position, grasp arm caps and slide or pivot（绕点旋转） in any direction.
you elbows should stay close to your sides and your wrists（手腕） straight.

--- Seat depth（深度？） ---
Lift lever and hold.
Slide seat forward or back, and release level to lock.
With your back against the chair, you should have 5cm - 7cm of space
between the back of your knees and the seat edge.

--- Upper back force ---
Turn the knob forward to increase tension（张力、紧张程度）.
Turn the knob backward to decrease tension.

Wrinkles（褶皱） on leather upholstery（内饰） and natural and expected.
*Optional features (may not be included in your chair)

Leap is SCS Indoor Advantage(TM) certified（被鉴定的） for indoor air quality.

